@startuml log-loading-workflow

title LogViewer - Log File Loading Workflow

actor User
participant MainWindow
participant Parser
participant EventsContainer
participant UIModel
participant EventsTableView

User -> MainWindow: Load Log File
MainWindow -> Parser: ParseFile(path)
activate Parser
Parser -> EventsContainer: Create event batch
Parser -> Parser: Parse file\n(XML/CSV)
note right of Parser
    Converts raw file data
    into LogEvent objects
end note
Parser --> EventsContainer: AddEventBatch([events])
deactivate Parser

EventsContainer -> EventsContainer: Lock (shared_mutex)
EventsContainer -> EventsContainer: Add events to storage
EventsContainer -> EventsContainer: Update indices
EventsContainer -> UIModel: NotifyDataChanged()
deactivate EventsContainer

UIModel -> EventsTableView: Update model
activate EventsTableView
EventsTableView -> EventsTableView: Refresh virtual view
note right of EventsTableView
    Virtual scrolling:
    Only renders visible rows
end note
EventsTableView --> User: Display log entries
deactivate EventsTableView

note over MainWindow
    Entire operation is non-blocking
    Parser runs in background thread
end note

@enduml
